<hw>Belles-let"tres</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[F.]</ety> <def>Polite or elegant literature; the humanities; --
used somewhat vaguely for literary works in which imagination and taste
are predominant.</def>⟦br⟧
